    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Note-of-Bubble-Collisions"><a href="#Note-of-Bubble-Collisions" class="headerlink" title="Note of Bubble Collisions"></a>Note of Bubble Collisions</h2><h4 id="Dynamic-of-false-vacuum-bubbles-in-Brans-Dicke-theory"><a href="#Dynamic-of-false-vacuum-bubbles-in-Brans-Dicke-theory" class="headerlink" title="Dynamic of false vacuum bubbles in Brans-Dicke theory"></a>Dynamic of false vacuum bubbles in Brans-Dicke theory</h4><p>Brans-Dicke theory 是一种scalar-tensor theory 的理论框架，引力的相互作用可以由scalar场调节。</p><p>关于引力的一个最重要的直觉就是Mach’s 原则， 惯性与引力属性有整个宇宙的物质分布决定。</p><p>在这篇文章里，G是时间的函数 G（t）, t又是宇宙的density 和size的函数。所以G由scalar场决定。</p><p>所以，bubble内部是brans-dicke 场 $\phi$, 外部是Einstein gravity.</p><p>​           内部是stable de Sitter space, outside is stable Schwarzschild space.</p><hr><h4 id="False-vacuum-bubble-nucleation-due-to-a-nonminimally-coupled-scalar-field"><a href="#False-vacuum-bubble-nucleation-due-to-a-nonminimally-coupled-scalar-field" class="headerlink" title="False vacuum bubble nucleation due to a nonminimally coupled scalar field"></a>False vacuum bubble nucleation due to a nonminimally coupled scalar field</h4><p>今天和wonwoo讨论了一下，这个时间段发生的真是太早了，z=10000，wonwoo因为想使得由true to fault 的变化，想让这个过程发生在inflation之前，这就没有了让他来做dark energy的动力。只能往引力波上搞了。</p><p>这篇文章里提到了几处由fault 的能量比true的低，所以有可能有相变的方法，但在action的变换并没有非常有效的解释由来。他建议我去读转换到Jordan frame的文章。</p><p>而且这篇有点错误，去读 nucleation of vacuum bubbles of a scalar-gravitating scalar field 的计算。</p><p>之后给我一篇f(R)的文章，觉得可以把 DEGB theory 套进proca, 嗯。。我再看看吧</p><p><a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2012.15625.pdf" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2012.15625.pdf</a> 荣根cai,</p><p>Magnetic field and gravitational waves from the first-order Phase Transition</p><img src="C:\Users\yinlu\Desktop\wonwoo\cai.png" alt="cai" style="zoom:60%;"><p><a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2007.15586.pdf" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2007.15586.pdf</a><